  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The land of bears breed mighty shinobi, and due to this vitality you're able to integrate Star Chakra throughout your entire chakra network. </p><p>Starting at 3rd level, you have resistance to Chakra Damage. Effects that would reduce your chakra are halved, and if an effect would allow a creature to absorb chakra as a result of damaging or reducing your own, that creature instead takes force damage equal to the amount it would have gained.</p><p>At 15th level, Star Chakra has overcharged your natural resilience, granting you advantage on Constitution saving throws against jutsu and conditions.</p>",
